*Riba* je vrsta životinje koja se nalazi u vodi (Fish is a type of animal that lives in water).
U nasem restoranu postoji mnogo jela sa *ribom* (In our restaurant there are many dishes with fish).
*Riba* se često konzumira u našoj zemlji (Fish is often consumed in our country).
Moj tata voli da peče *ribe* na roštilju (My dad likes to grill fish).
Moje dete voli da se igra sa *ribama* u akvarijumu (My child likes to play with the fish in the aquarium).